videos.headline: Oregon's Chris Boucher showing off his length early with this rim defense
Oregon's Chris Boucher spikes the Montana layup attempt off the head of his own teammate for his third block

videos.description: 1H (9:00) MONT Ahmaad Rorie made Layup. Assisted by Walter Wright.
videos.headline: Montana's W. Wright steals the ball then threads the needle leading to an A. Rorie fast break Layup

videos.description: 1H (5:08) ORE Chris Boucher made Jumper. Assisted by Dylan Ennis.
videos.headline: Oregon's C. Boucher blocks another shot then recives the no look pass from D. Ennis for the layup

videos.description: 1H (1:56) MONT Fabijan Krslovic made Jumper. Assisted by Sayeed Pridgett.
videos.headline: Montana's S. Pridgett draws three defenders under the basket and finds F. Krslovic for the and-1 layup

videos.description: Payton Pritchard misses a 3-pointer, but Chris Boucher is there for the putback slam for Oregon.
videos.headline: Oregon's Boucher rises over everyone for putback slam
Oregon's C. Boucher denies another layup for his fifth Block of the night
